title: Brian Lawlor's Zwischenzug
description: Brian Lawlor is a composer, multi-instrumentalist, and conductor living in Jersey City, NJ.  He earned a B.M. in Music Composition from Cornish College of the Arts, an M.M. from SUNY Purchase, and studied at the Royal Conservatory of Music in Den Haag, Netherlands. Mr. Lawlor has received grants from Jack Straw Productions, Atlantic Center for the Arts, and his music has been performed throughout North America, Europe and China.
author: Brian Lawlor
